</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="362" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="362">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="362">
Because taxonomy of the longicornis-group is quite difficult (
<bibRefCitation pageId="15" pageNumber="362">Prous et al. 2011b</bibRefCitation>
) and the corresponding female remains to be found yet, additional material is needed to describe and name this presumably new species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
